data.description: Welcome home to 831 Magnolia St. This 3 bedroom charmer is sure to steal your heart! Located near HEB, an abundance of restaurants, and shopping, you'll love the easy access to Highway 288. Some of the amazing features of this home include two living areas, an attached garage, oversized driveway, and a large backyard featuring a patio and outdoor storage shed. There is a remodeled addition in the back of the home that was completed in December 2021. Enjoy summer evenings in your backyard that is perfect for entertaining! Schedule your showing and come and see what  this great home has to offer.
